channel.title: How can you tell if your IP banned?
channel.description: How can i tell if im IP banned and for how long it is for my example it wont let me go on any server does that mean im IP banned it wont let me go on the server pkfrenzy.no-ip.biz (really good server) so what do i do people???????

item.title: How can you tell if your IP banned?
item.dc:creator: @strengthxlx strengthxlx
item.description:
@strengthxlx wrote:

If it says “No response from server” you’re ip banned. if it says “your account has been disabled etc…” you’re banned… if it says “error connecting to server” most likely server isn’t up.
